                     <interp inst="t18220911-187-person1804" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took him in charge; he begged for mercy, and said it was his first offence.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I never took them. I went away from my barrow, and was taking the liquor to my sister. I did not beg for mercy.</p>
